{"tid":1691406,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[建議] 香城online2.0 和理非係時候再進化","createTime":"2019-11-03T15:47:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T18:01:01.000Z","uid":268268,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bc411957e86498693bfcc9a525ecb73482455215","tid":1691406,"uid":268268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:47:35.000Z","msg":"最近有唔少Post都係話緊一眾和理非玩家，一聽到有黑狗就即刻跑<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">一來係怕催淚彈</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">二來係驚畀狗咬</span><br />\n<br />\n先講第一，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">最大問題係和理非玩家乜防裝都冇</span><br />\n<br />\n好坦白咁講，催淚彈對勇武嘅手足嚟講根本唔成威脅(鬼國製嘅另計)，五個月以嚟都已經慣曬，而且我相信啲狗都明白呢一點<br />\n所以<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">催淚彈其實係用嚟對付後排嘅玩家，因為知你哋乜裝都冇</span></span><br />\n只要你哋一走，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">前線嘅勇武玩家全部就會即刻變曬做condom</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以各位和理非玩家不如試下升級，<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">每人都最基本帶個3M 3200 單罐式豬嘴+泳鏡</span></span></strong>？ 即使你唔衝都唔使驚催淚彈啦<br />\n3200 五金舖$100有找<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EFbj8MT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEFbj8MT.jpg&h=7e4b84b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二，<span style=\"color: red;\">係驚俾狗咬</span>。<br />\n有無數咁多個玩家都有講過人數多就安全，呢一句嘢絕對適用喺進攻上<br />\n大家可以睇下以下嗰張圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZMj9MyF.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZMj9MyF.gif&h=7a051647&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相信大家都會好想睇到下面嘅畫面再次發生，大家要記住，啲狗都會驚，尤其是咁多人同時向前衝。<br />\n和理非玩家可能會話：<br />\n「我唔敢打狗喎，點衝呀？」<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">傻啦，咁多勇武玩家企喺你前面幫你擋緊子彈，你擔多把遮都擋到好多嘢啦，你淨係陪手足一齊跑上前已經好好啦</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁當然可以一齊打怪嘅話就更好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有，平時有狗車衝過來大家就一定驚到即刻跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實除非係裝修小隊行動，基本上在場嘅玩家數量之少都會有幾百、千人<br />\n<br />\n我哋試下嚟計下數(有錯請指出)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n一架豬籠可以裝16隻黑狗，一架EU衝鋒可以裝6至7隻<br />\n<br />\n數學題：兩架EU加一架豬籠，有幾多隻黑狗？<br />\n16+7*2 = <span style=\"color: red;\">30</span><br />\n兩架EU加兩架豬籠，有幾多隻狗？<br />\n16*2 + 7*2 = <span style=\"color: red;\">46</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1000香城玩家 v.s. 46黑狗</span></span><br />\n其實點樣數都好，黑狗嘅數量係點都唔夠我哋玩家多，佢哋仲驚過我哋<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">各位和理非玩家，嚟到第五個月，我哋一齊再進化好唔好？</span></span><br />\n<br />\nTLTR ：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">和理非玩家聽到有狗就跑<br />\n原因：1. 驚催淚彈  2. 驚畀狗咬<br />\n結果：勇武=Condom</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">解決/進化方法<br />\n1. 升級防裝：3M 3200+泳鏡<br />\n2. 前面有勇武擋子彈+黑狗數目唔夠我哋多 = <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">和理非陪衝衝子一齊向前衝</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非進化！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">頭盔：我打機咋，唔鼓勵暴力架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"c1797f98686e733d77e8f4dfa85366a51a92da02","tid":1691406,"uid":272805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:59:02.000Z","msg":"得閒指定去某d商場幫襯下有冇得諗？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1691418\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1691418</a>"},{"pid":"276bc005312d6552d6a729adf057beda4fba5a03","tid":1691406,"uid":268268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T16:22:55.000Z","msg":"十連推"},{"pid":"348d943da1a0fc6199bfcfc2ea1cda08ee01ca33","tid":1691406,"uid":268268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T16:23:06.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"a26de5b1107d369b7c755b34c103bcf27d0fec77","tid":1691406,"uid":268268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T17:55:03.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"def3b7f11ef88fcbdcd85266fddea53e1293c5d7","tid":1691406,"uid":268268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T17:55:13.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"28297571f5894b0928ff58107ebcab3db4d63b7f","tid":1691406,"uid":268268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T17:55:26.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"9f01db743b1c675d9eec10a1d7645a15702a73f8","tid":1691406,"uid":268268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T17:55:36.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"bad5a63631c84f8981fee30c33436f8788bcf58d","tid":1691406,"uid":268268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T17:57:38.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"26475008116f2a9b0b3745a454fa670494ac1686","tid":1691406,"uid":268268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T17:59:14.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"231e6bd5252407008e51e1ceb66bfa4cb6395a4b","tid":1691406,"uid":268268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T18:01:01.000Z","msg":"8"}]}